Entity User

Action perform_user_registration
  EventInput
    user_id   required
    email     required
  BusinessRules
    - user_id must not already exist (idempotency — first login only)
  Steps
    - Create User record
  SideEffects
    - None
  ActionResult
    user_id   string

Action perform_search_all
  EventInput
    query         required
    entity_types  optional
  BusinessRules
    - query must be at least 2 characters
  Steps
    - Execute PostgreSQL FTS query across all active Spaces owned by the user
    - Search targets per entity type:
        Task:           title, description
        Note:           title, body            (type = manual only)
        Activity:       name, description
        CalendarEntry:  title, description
        TaskComment:    content
    - Filter: only Active records (status = Active or non-archived)
    - Filter: only records within Spaces owned by the requesting user
    - Rank results by ts_rank relevance score
    - Each result includes path:  SpaceName / EntityType / Title
  SideEffects
    - None
  ActionResult
    results       object[]
      entity_type   string    Task | Note | Activity | CalendarEntry | TaskComment
      entity_id     UUID
      title         string    display title of the match
      excerpt       string    snippet with match highlighted
      path          string    e.g. "Casa / Task / Pago hipoteca — Abril 2026"
      score         float     relevance score from ts_rank
    total_count   integer
